0 NETHERWORLD~
{128}
                               The Netherworld
{300}
This area is the mystical Realm of the evil dead, the playground of demons
and the origin of the power of necromancery. It exists under the region
known as Avernus and encompasses the remaining 8 layers of Hell:
Dis, Minauros, Phlegethos, Stygia, Malbolge, Maladomini, Cania and Nessus.
Avernus is ruled by the pit devil Belial. The other 8 layers are ruled by
the dark eight: Furcas, Baalzephon, Zimimar, Zapan, Zaebos, Corin, Dagos,
and Pearza. These greater devils have equipment of great value to those
of evil orientation.

You must be strong to enter this realm of evil. Anyone with a weak frame
of mind would surely be killed by an overflow of negative energy.  Only
warlocks are capable of understanding the power of the Netherworld and
are therefore able to enter.

